{"tid":149998,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"坐巴士優先座被鬧大嬸 廿幾歲日女怒毆少年","createTime":"2017-03-09T16:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T02:36:38.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca473ddae78e334d369f9b392750b89f41869684","tid":149998,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:29:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170309&amp;guid=56403347&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170309%26guid%3D56403347%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=d99584b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170309%26guid%3D56403347%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=fad62184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170309&amp;guid=56403347&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n日本北海道札幌一名廿多歲女子，因為坐巴士優先座而遭一名十多歲少年勸止，2人先發生口角，後來女子向少年動粗，遭警方送交檢察當局處理。<br />\n<br />\n事發在上月18日，片段在網上廣傳，當時女子坐在少年左邊的優先座，少年就叫她不要霸佔優先座，2人繼而口角。女子怒氣沖沖走向少年身邊破口大罵，一手就將他的鴨舌帽撥開，然後扯住他的頭髮往後扯，再將自己的臉龐湊近少年，怒罵：「別開玩笑了，臭小子！」<br />\n<br />\n司機透過車上廣播系統勸止2人，但女子已情緒失控，一度走向車門又折返，再毆打少年頭部。少年遇襲後道：「司機，可以報警嗎？」女子大叫：「真吵，錯的是你吧？誰是大嬸啊。說說看吧！」<br />\n<br />\n少年事後報警求助，警方昨以暴行罪名將女子送交檢察當局跟進，女子亦都表示：「被人說是『大嬸』，怒氣沖心。」<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9VCAv6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9VCAv6p.jpg&h=a34699b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97a9cfad0c7a631cf85f9ef0bbdad43d85bff3b8","tid":149998,"uid":12782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:31:55.000Z","msg":"肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039596ac2bf17b270eda80843dd2363d55f853ac","tid":149998,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:32:26.000Z","msg":"on9青年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfce5e12119e9416d027bde87159a9ec34663f0","tid":149998,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T02:36:38.000Z","msg":"好撚肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}